{"type":"section","nativeType":"section","number":"8922","heading":"Agricultural biosecurity grant program","label":"8922 Agricultural biosecurity grant program","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s8922","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t7/ch114/schII","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft7%2Fs8922","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":["Editorial Notes","Codificationand enacted identical sections. was repealed by .Pub. L. 110–234Pub. L. 110–246Pub. L. 110–234section 4(a) of Pub. L. 110–246","Amendments2018—Subsec. (e)(2). substituted “2023” for “2018”.Pub. L. 115–3342014—Subsec. (e). struck out “sums as are necessary” after “appropriated”, substituted “section—” for “section for each of fiscal years 2008 through 2012, to remain available until expended.”, and added pars. (1) and (2).Pub. L. 113–79","Statutory Notes and Related Subsidiaries","Effective DateEnactment of this section and repeal of by effective , the date of enactment of , see , set out as a note under .Pub. L. 110–234Pub. L. 110–246Pub. L. 110–234section 4 of Pub. L. 110–246section 8701 of this titleMay 22, 2008","Definition of “Secretary”“Secretary” as meaning the Secretary of Agriculture, see .section 8701 of this title"],"amendments":["Amendments2018—Subsec. (e)(2). substituted “2023” for “2018”.Pub. L. 115–3342014—Subsec. (e). struck out “sums as are necessary” after “appropriated”, substituted “section—” for “section for each of fiscal years 2008 through 2012, to remain available until expended.”, and added pars. (1) and (2).Pub. L. 113–79"],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"subsection","nativeType":"subsection","number":"a","heading":"Competitive grant program","label":"a Competitive grant program","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s8922/a","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t7/s8922","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft7%2Fs8922%2Fa","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"The Secretary shall establish a competitive grant program to promote the development of teaching programs in agriculture, veterinary medicine, and disciplines closely allied to the food and agriculture system to increase the number of trained individuals with an expertise in agricultural biosecurity.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"subsection","nativeType":"subsection","number":"b","heading":"Eligibility","label":"b Eligibility","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s8922/b","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t7/s8922","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft7%2Fs8922%2Fb","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"1","heading":null,"label":"1","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s8922/b/1","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t7/s8922/b","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft7%2Fs8922%2Fb%2F1","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"an accredited school of veterinary medicine; or","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"2","heading":null,"label":"2","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s8922/b/2","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t7/s8922/b","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft7%2Fs8922%2Fb%2F2","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"A","heading":null,"label":"A","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s8922/b/2/A","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t7/s8922/b/2","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft7%2Fs8922%2Fb%2F2%2FA","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"comparative medicine;","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"B","heading":null,"label":"B","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s8922/b/2/B","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t7/s8922/b/2","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft7%2Fs8922%2Fb%2F2%2FB","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"veterinary science; or","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"C","heading":null,"label":"C","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s8922/b/2/C","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t7/s8922/b/2","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft7%2Fs8922%2Fb%2F2%2FC","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"agricultural biosecurity.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]}]}]},{"type":"subsection","nativeType":"subsection","number":"c","heading":"Preference","label":"c Preference","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s8922/c","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t7/s8922","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft7%2Fs8922%2Fc","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"1","heading":null,"label":"1","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s8922/c/1","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t7/s8922/c","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft7%2Fs8922%2Fc%2F1","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"to increase the number of veterinarians or individuals with advanced degrees in food and agriculture disciplines who are trained in agricultural biosecurity practice areas;","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"2","heading":null,"label":"2","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s8922/c/2","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t7/s8922/c","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft7%2Fs8922%2Fc%2F2","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"to increase research capacity in areas of agricultural biosecurity; or","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"3","heading":null,"label":"3","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s8922/c/3","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t7/s8922/c","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft7%2Fs8922%2Fc%2F3","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"to fill critical agricultural biosecurity shortage situations outside of the Federal Government.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]}]},{"type":"subsection","nativeType":"subsection","number":"d","heading":"Use of funds","label":"d Use of funds","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s8922/d","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t7/s8922","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft7%2Fs8922%2Fd","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"1","heading":"In general","label":"1 In general","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s8922/d/1","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t7/s8922/d","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft7%2Fs8922%2Fd%2F1","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"A","heading":null,"label":"A","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s8922/d/1/A","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t7/s8922/d/1","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft7%2Fs8922%2Fd%2F1%2FA","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"costs associated with the acquisition of equipment and other capital costs relating to the expansion of food, agriculture, and veterinary medicine teaching programs in agricultural biosecurity;","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"B","heading":null,"label":"B","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s8922/d/1/B","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t7/s8922/d/1","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft7%2Fs8922%2Fd%2F1%2FB","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"capital costs associated with the expansion of academic programs that offer postgraduate training for veterinarians or concurrent training f